### Order Management System API Tests

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Create a new order
POST {{baseUrl}}/order
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buyerId": "user-id-here",
  "paymentMethod": "credit_card",
  "shippingAddress": "123 Main St, City, State, 12345",
  "billingAddress": "123 Main St, City, State, 12345",
  "notes": "Please deliver during business hours",
  "taxAmount": 10.50,
  "shippingAmount": 5.99,
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "productId": "product-id-1",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 29.99
    },
    {
      "productId": "product-id-2", 
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 49.99
    }
  ]
}

### Get order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/order-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get order by order number
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/number/ORD-20250101-ABC12345
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get my orders (for logged-in user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/my-orders?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all orders (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get seller orders (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/seller/seller-id-here?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update order status (admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/order/order-id-here/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "shipped",
  "notes": "Order has been shipped via UPS"
}

### Update payment status (admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/order/order-id-here/payment-status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentStatus": "paid",
  "notes": "Payment confirmed via credit card"
}

### Cancel order (buyer only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/order/order-id-here/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get order statistics (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/statistics?sellerId=seller-id-here&startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
